</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre>    <span class="nt">&lt;main&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;section&gt;</span>
            <span class="nt">&lt;h2&gt;</span>Benvenuti<span class="nt">&lt;/h2&gt;</span>
            <span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>Questo è il contenuto principale della pagina.<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;/section&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;article&gt;</span>
